Package imac

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Camera
    Camera class refers to the camera of the application It moves according to the player position
    Engine
    Engine class controls the entire application.
    Main
    Main is the main PApplet App class.
    Menu
    Menu class displays the menu of the application It allows to navigate between each level.
    MIDIController
    MIDIController allows to interact with a physical controller Connect a physical controller Get and set some informations about it Class import @see themidibus library Optimize for a Arturia Beatstep @see Arturia website for more information
    Object3D
    Object3D class is an helper tool to control a PShape model
    Rocket
    Rocket describes the playable character class".
